{
  "id": 5745430754230272,
  "name": "ARIA Notify API",
  "summary": "ariaNotify provides a JavaScript API that enables content authors to directly tell a screen reader what to read. \n\nariaNotify improves reliability and developer control compared to ARIA live regions, allowing for announcing changes not tied to DOM updates. This enables more consistent and ergonomic accessibility experiences across dynamic web applications. Iframe usage of this feature can be controlled via a permission policy \"aria-notify\".",
